{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5393", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5393/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5393/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5393/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/datalad/datalad/issues/5393", "id": 797392574, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU3OTczOTI1NzQ=", "number": 5393, "title": "AnnexJsonProtocol cannot handle large JSON lines", "user": {"login": "mih", "id": 136479, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEzNjQ3OQ==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/136479?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih", "html_url": "https://github.com/mih", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 447185719, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw0NDcxODU3MTk=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/labels/regression", "name": "regression", "color": "fc8387", "default": false, "description": ""}, {"id": 1782622781, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxNzgyNjIyNzgx", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/labels/severity-important", "name": "severity-important", "color": "cc0000", "default": false, "description": "major effect on the usability of a package, without rendering it completely unusable to everyone"}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 5, "created_at": "2021-01-30T11:06:28Z", "updated_at": "2021-03-19T14:27:21Z", "closed_at": "2021-03-19T14:27:21Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Due to a coding error I have (erm, it turns out there is no coding error -- see below).\r\n\r\n```\r\n[git-annex] % wc -l < uuid.log\r\n34869\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis file is 3.8M. git-annex in general, and `git annex info --json` in particular, happily works with this, but not DataLad.\r\n\r\n```\r\n% python3 -c \"import datalad.api as dl; dl.Dataset('.').repo.repo_info()\"\r\n...\r\n[ERROR] Received undecodable JSON output\r\n...\r\nTraceback (most recent call last):\r\n  File \"<string>\", line 1, in <module>\r\n  File \"/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/datalad/support/annexrepo.py\", line 2460, in repo_info\r\n    assert(len(json_records) == 1)\r\nAssertionError\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis seems due to the implementation of the `AnnexJsonProtocol`. `git annex info --json` will report all of this information in a single line. With 3.8MB of text, we seem to hit a buffer limit and only attempt to process an incomplete JSON records, and eventually blow when nothing intelligible comes back from the protocol.", "closed_by": {"login": "kyleam", "id": 1297788, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEyOTc3ODg=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1297788?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam", "html_url": "https://github.com/kyleam", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kyleam/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5393/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/5393/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null}